\subsubsection{Comprehending Tongues (G-2)}
d147 7
a153 8
\emph{Range:} Self \\
\emph{Duration:} 10 minutes + 10/rank \\
\emph{Experience multiple:} 150 \\
\emph{Base Chance:} 20\% \\
\emph{Resist:} May not be resistedne \\
\emph{Target:} Self \\
\emph{Storage:} Potion \\
\emph{Effects:}
d155 7
a161 10

Enables the Adept to speak and understand one language at a rank
equal to 3 + 1/4 full ranks the Adept has attained in this spell.
The language may be nominated by name, or by nominating a target
sentient capable of communicating verbally, and wishing to speak
the language of that entity. This allows those spells that
require the Adept to be understood by a target to be effective.
This spell allows the Adept to be understood, but confers no
other bonuses. (It will not function in the area of a Confusion
of Tongues spell.)
d166 6
