non-sentient entities within range that do not resist to be
pacified. Such entites must make a check against 1 \x willpower -
 rank of spell to attack the Adept, and a check against 2 x
willpower to attack the Adept's companions. The creature's
reaction roll is increased by 10\% + 2/rank, such that the
d317 2
a318 2
spell. If a soothed entity is attacked, or the Adept ceases to
play and/or sing, the spell ceases to be in effect. 
