\end{spelldesc}
The Adept plays a song that affects one willing entity (+1/3 or
fraction ranks) causing them to drift into a normal sleep. All
affected targets fall asleep in 4 minutes (-10 seconds/Rank, minimum
of 30 seconds). Targets will remain asleep until disturbed or they
awaken normally. This enchantment may not be cast in combat. The
resulting sleep is healing and refreshing allowing the targets to
regain 1 + 1/5 full ranks more fatigue per hour while under its
effect.

